OL,3,CPlay inspired by Windrush Scandal
OL,4,Cbrings UK tour to Manchester
OL,6,FITV News' Sam Taylor went to meet the
OL,7,Fcast and crew as they prepare for the
OL,8,Ffinal stop of their tour.
OL,10,FA play that tells the story of the
OL,11,FWindrush Scandal from the perspective
OL,12,Fof a group of pensioners is being
OL,13,Fstaged in Manchester.
OL,15,FThe Windrush Warriors, which was
OL,16,Fwritten by and stars Coronation Street
OL,17,Factor Nicola Gardner, is a "multi-
OL,18,Fethnic comedy drama" that has toured
OL,19,Fthe country telling the story of the
OL,20,FWindrush generation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
