OL,6,FThe Windrush generation are those who
OL,7,Farrived in the UK from Caribbean
OL,8,Fcountries between 1948 and 1973.
OL,10,FMany took up jobs in the NHS and other
OL,11,Fsectors affected by Britain's post-war
OL,12,Flabour shortage.
OL,14,FIt is called Windrush because a ship
OL,15,Fcalled The Empire Windrush brought one
OL,16,Fof the first large groups of Caribbean
OL,17,Fpeople to the UK on June 22, 1948.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
