OL,6,FAt the time, the Caribbean was a part
OL,7,Fof the British commonwealth which
OL,8,Fmeant those who arrived were
OL,9,Fautomatically British subjects and
OL,10,Ffree to permanently live and work in
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FBut, the scandal began to surface in
OL,14,F2018 after it emerged, due to changes
OL,15,Fin the immigration system, thousands
OL,16,Fof Commonwealth citizens, many of whom
OL,17,Fwere from the Windrush generation,
OL,18,Fwere wrongly detained, deported and
OL,19,Fdenied legal rights.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
