OL,6,FIt was through talking to the people
OL,7,Fwhose lives were upturned by the
OL,8,Fscandal that Nicola was inspired to
OL,9,Fwrite The Windrush Warriors.
OL,11,FNicola said: "I spoke to them first
OL,12,Fhand and got their accounts, and that
OL,13,Fmade me sit down and write this play."
OL,15,FThe show's director, John Klark,
OL,16,Fadded: "It's been a real honour to
OL,17,Fbring those real life stories to the
OL,18,Fstage - this has happened to real
OL,19,Fpeople and it's important to keep
OL,20,Fthose stories alive and in the
OL,21,Fforefront of people's minds."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
