OL,6,FThe show features a diverse cast and
OL,7,Fcrew, including Jewish, Irish, and
OL,8,FAfro-Caribbean actors who all bring
OL,9,Ftheir lived experiences to the role.
OL,11,FLukeland Chambers plays Brother Leroy,
OL,12,Fa "boisterous but fun" pensioner who
OL,13,Farrived in the UK on the HMT Empire
OL,14,FWindrush.
OL,16,FLukeland said: "His job really is to
OL,17,Frally the troops, keep everyone
OL,18,Ffocused but also have fun while also
OL,19,Fsupplying a lot of rum."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
