OL,6,FAs the son of two members of the
OL,7,FWindrush generation, Lukeland was able
OL,8,Fto draw on the experiences of his
OL,9,Fparents for the role.
OL,11,FHe said: "They are the Windrush
OL,12,Fgeneration so I've often heard stories
OL,13,Fof how they were treated when they
OL,14,Ffirst arrived - so when I got the role
OL,15,Fit was a great reason to delve into
OL,16,Fthat and use it for my character."
OL,18,FHis fellow actor, Tommy C. Carey, was
OL,19,Fable to draw on his Irish heritage to
OL,20,Frelate to members of the Windrush
OL,21,Fgeneration.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
