OL,6,FHe said: "As an Irish person, when we
OL,7,Farrived in the 80s we weren't really
OL,8,Fwelcome... so for that reason I could
OL,9,Freally relate to the Windrush
OL,10,FGeneration."
OL,12,FThe Windrush scandal and compensation
OL,13,Fscheme was introduced in April 2019,
OL,14,Fbut five years on many have struggled
OL,15,Fto get the money they are entitled to.
OL,17,FAnthony Brown is a lawyer that
OL,18,Frepresents and supports members of the
OL,19,FWindrush Generation, and is also a
OL,20,Ffounding member of Windrush Legal
OL,21,FDefenders CIC in Moss Side.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
