OL,6,FHe said: "A lot of trauma has taken
OL,7,Fplace... The compensation scheme has
OL,8,Fbeen introduced but it's very
OL,9,Fconfusing and a lot of people don't
OL,10,Ftrust them."
OL,12,FHowever, Anthony Brown feels real
OL,13,Fprogress is being made to right the
OL,14,Fwrongs of the Windrush scandal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
