OL,6,FHe said: "We've made a number of
OL,7,Frecommendations, but we've also
OL,8,Frealised that the community has faced
OL,9,Fdetrimental factors in other areas
OL,10,Fsuch as education, health, art, and
OL,11,Fthey all widen the disparity and add
OL,12,Fto the trauma.
OL,14,F"And we've found the Home Office is
OL,15,Flistening to that - and they are
OL,16,Fwilling to work with communities up
OL,17,Fand down the country."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
