OL,6,FOne of the recommendations the
OL,7,FWindrush Legal Defenders CIC made to
OL,8,Fthe Home Office involved encouraging
OL,9,Fart and theatre to help bring
OL,10,Fcommunities together and provide
OL,11,Ffunding for projects like the Windrush
OL,12,FWarriors.
OL,14,FAnthony said: "These communities have
OL,15,Ftheir own art, like Caribbean Carnival
OL,16,For sound systems, and that can bring
OL,17,Fpeople together. But we should also
OL,18,Fencourage things like plays and
OL,19,Ftheatre to help tell our story both in
OL,20,Fand out of our communities."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
